# Rule 10: Unauthorized User Added to Privileged Group
# --------------------------------------------------
# Description: Detects when a user account is added to a sensitive security group 
# like 'Administrators', 'Domain Admins', or 'Enterprise Admins'.
# 
# MITRE ATT&CK: T1078.002 (Valid Accounts: Domain Accounts)
# Severity: High
# 
# Logic (Sigma-style):
#   - EventID: 4732 (A member was added to a security-enabled local group)
#   - TargetGroupName: 'Administrators'
#   - EventID: 4728 (A member was added to a security-enabled global group)
# 
# Log Source: Windows Security Log (Account Management)
